## US-073: Procedural Path Generation — Complete

**Files created/modified:**
- `game/world/pathGenerator.ts` — pure path generator (200 lines)
- `game/world/pathGenerator.test.ts` — 28 tests covering all exported functions
- `game/world/ChunkManager.ts` — wired into `loadChunk`

**Architecture:**
- `isLandmarkChunk` — chunk (0,0) is always the tutorial village; all others stochastically seeded at 15% probability
- `getLandmarkLocalPos` / `getLandmarkType` — seeded position near chunk center; village only at origin
- `bezierPoint` — quadratic Bézier evaluation with seeded perpendicular control-point offset for natural-looking curves
- `carveSplineIntoHeightmap` — O(V×S) scan with cosine falloff blend; mutates the heightmap in-place before the ECS entity is created, so carved terrain is baked at birth
- `generatePathsForChunk` — main entry: checks 4 cardinal neighbors for landmarks, generates road paths for villages and trail paths for other landmarks, creates `PathSegmentComponent` entities

**Quality:** `npx tsc --noEmit` → 0 errors | `npx jest --no-coverage` → 2174 tests, 0 failures

